title: Always Sometimes Monsters
description:
Name: Always Sometimes Monsters
Year: 2014
Kind: Wineskin
Genre: Indie, RPG
Developer: Vagabond Dog, Devolver Digital
Rating: 73/100 on Metacritic

Description:
Set out on a cross-country journey to win back the love of your life and endure the hardship of making story-defining choices that affect your life and the lives of those around you.

Instructions: Unzip and Play

Warning:
Always Sometimes Monsters has content dealing with racism, sexism, homophobia, transphobia, mental health, sexual assault, child abuse, animal abuse, drug abuse, and suicide.

OS: Tested and working on Mavericks and Yosemite

Show your appreciation by seeding and support the developers by buying the game.
